| 
| THIS DRIVER IS A DEVELOPMENT RELEASE FOR A DEVELOPMENT KERNEL.  DO NOT
| USE IN A PRODUCTION ENVIRONMENT.
| 
| However, I've used Donald Becker's rtl8139 driver in the past without
